data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom two story home with over 2,100+ finished sq. *New roof on house and garage 10/23* Hardwood flooring, spacious room sizes, updated cherrywood kitchen cabinets and countertops, lighting under cabinets, newer fixtures, SS appliances, updated 1/2 bath, updated windows, four bedrooms on one level, large patio for entertaining and heated oversized two stall garage, new wiring, and more. This home offers so much space in a great location with a view of North Lake!
